<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .alert {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
      color: #856404;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .details {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #dc3545;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="alert">
      <h2>New Login Detected</h2>
    </div>
    
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>We detected a new login to your RinaWarp account. Here are the details:</p>

    <div class="details">
      <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
      <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
      <p><strong>Device:</strong> {{deviceInfo.browser}} on {{deviceInfo.os}}</p>
      <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{deviceInfo.ip}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>If this was you, you can ignore this email. If you don't recognize this activity:</p>

    <a href="{{securitySettingsUrl}}" class="button">Review Security Settings</a>

    <p>We recommend:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Changing your password immediately</li>
      <li>Enabling two-factor authentication if you haven't already</li>
      <li>Reviewing your recent account activity</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent by RinaWarp. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p>If you did not initiate this login, please contact support immediately.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
